title: Delhi reports 91 new COVID-19 positive cases in last 24 hrs; total rises to 384
description: Of the 384 cases, 58 had recent foreign travel history and 38 contracted the virus after coming in contact with them. Delhi chief minister Arvind Kejriwal said community spread of the virus is not taking place in Delhi yet and there is no need to panic as the…
